data.description: Newly remodeled ranch plan home in great location! Situated on a corner lot, in a cul-de-sac with large front yard and covered entry. Brand new laminate flooring throughout the main living spaces. Spacious eat-in kitchen features all new white cabinets, butcher block counters, built in bar area with open shelving, pantry closet, and all new stainless appliances. Open concept living/dining area with vaulted ceilings. New lighting & new paint throughout. Walk out from living room to the wood deck and fully fenced over sized, corner lot backyard. So much space and great mountain views! The primary bedroom is separate at the back of the home with vaulted ceilings, built-in window seat, walk in closet, and updated attached full bathroom. The bathroom features double sinks, new vanity, modern lighting & mirrors, tiled shower surround, laminate floors, and convenient built-in storage. Two more good sized bedrooms, another updated full bathroom and laundry space complete this clean, modern home. New AC in 2019, new roof and new water heater in 2018! Home is located near Mesa Ridge shopping, neighborhood parks, hiking trails, and military bases.
